00:10:07.260 --> 00:10:09.290
You decided to leave
the high-powered job

00:10:09.290 --> 00:10:10.590
at the State Department.

00:10:10.590 --> 00:10:14.000
And kind of, you know,
downshift, let's call it.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.340
Leaning out, whatever
