00:10:16.340 --> 00:10:18.550
And I have to know that
your version of leaning out.

00:10:18.550 --> 00:10:21.140
Involves being a tenured
Princeton professor.

00:10:21.140 --> 00:10:24.760
Writing a best-selling, <i>New
York Times</i>, best-seller book.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:27.640
Founding a think-tank
here in Washington.

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:29.460
And you've got another book
coming out in the spring.

00:10:29.460 --> 00:10:31.040
