I'm going to write an
<i>Atlantic</i> article.

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:58.410
And I'm going to tell you
what it was really like.

00:10:58.410 --> 00:11:00.930
That mom was never home.

00:11:00.930 --> 00:11:02.740
So I am very high-energy.

00:11:02.740 --> 00:11:04.140
No question.

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:09.320
And yes. So what -- but
