00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:10.990
I still work a lot.

00:11:10.990 --> 00:11:12.870
I love my work.

00:11:12.870 --> 00:11:16.630
But there's a huge difference
between what I'm doing.

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:18.900
And taking that really big job.

00:11:18.900 --> 00:11:21.140
One more step up in
the State Department.

00:11:21.140 --> 00:11:24.620
I would have been an undersecretary
or a deputy secretary.

00:11:24.620 --> 00:11:28.080
One more step up as a
professor, or I'd been a dean.

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:30.200
I'd be a president of a University.

