my son's birthday.

00:11:37.170 --> 00:11:38.720
It's a period of vacation.

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:40.020
Whatever it is.

00:11:40.020 --> 00:11:42.340
What I'm doing, I'm
running an organization.

00:11:42.340 --> 00:11:44.790
