00:11:44.790 --> 00:11:46.520
So I can be here two days a week.

00:11:46.520 --> 00:11:48.460
But then be home at other times.

00:11:48.460 --> 00:11:50.690
I can adjust.

00:11:50.690 --> 00:11:54.220
When I needed to take my son to
