00:13:31.790 --> 00:13:35.630
and women can be lead
parents, and trade off.

00:13:35.630 --> 00:13:37.770
And the men who are lead parents.

00:13:37.770 --> 00:13:41.760
The reward is they get that special
relationship with their kids.

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:43.290
That women have traditionally had.

00:13:43.290 --> 00:13:45.540
And most of us don't
